    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hooks that are attached to the inside, back, or side walls of a fireplace, used for suspending pots and kettles over a fire or for holding implements.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
